Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:05.20,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,新たな火種が
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:08.63,Default,Nar,0,0,0,,{\fscx96}With that, a new threat endangers the tangled web Central is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.60,0:24:08.40,*Default-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,錯綜するセントラルに降りかかる
